From: Mats Loman <mats.loman@rte.se>
Date: 2026-07-15
Subject: [PATCH] ALSA: usb-audio: add UAC2 quirk for Avid/Digidesign Eleven Rack

The Avid/Digidesign Eleven Rack (0dba:b011) exposes an audio function whose
class-specific descriptors are standard USB Audio Class 2.0 -- standard
AudioControl/AudioStreaming subclasses, UAC2 protocol (0x20), a standard clock
model (clock selector 0x80 over sources 0x81/0x82/0x83), TYPE_I 32-bit PCM
format descriptors, and playback slaved to capture via implicit feedback. The
only non-standard detail is bInterfaceClass = 0xFF (vendor) on the audio
interfaces, which prevents snd-usb-audio from binding, so the device has MIDI
(hw:X,0) but no PCM on Linux.

Add a composite quirk that claims the vendor-class interfaces and drives them
through the standard UAC2 path: interface 1 as the mixer/clock/terminal control,
interfaces 3 and 4 as the streaming interfaces (6-channel playback on EP 0x03,
8-channel capture on EP 0x83, 32-bit, 44.1 kHz and up per the programmable
clock). Interface 2 remains standard USB-MIDI; interface 0 (DFU) is ignored and
left to userspace.

Signed-off-by: <run `git commit -s` to add your Signed-off-by line>
---
 sound/usb/quirks-table.h | 20 ++++++++++++++++++++
 1 file changed, 20 insertions(+)

diff --git a/sound/usb/quirks-table.h b/sound/usb/quirks-table.h
--- a/sound/usb/quirks-table.h
+++ b/sound/usb/quirks-table.h
@@ -3900,5 +3900,25 @@
 QUIRK_RME_DIGIFACE(0x3f8c),
 QUIRK_RME_DIGIFACE(0x3fa0),

+	/*
+	 * Avid/Digidesign Eleven Rack: UAC2 in all but bInterfaceClass (0xFF).
+	 * Force snd-usb-audio to claim + parse the vendor-class audio interfaces
+	 * as standard UAC2. See contrib/eleven-rack-alsa-quirk/ in the rackctl repo.
+	 */
+{
+	USB_DEVICE(0x0dba, 0xb011),
+	QUIRK_DRIVER_INFO {
+		.vendor_name = "Digidesign",
+		.product_name = "Eleven Rack",
+		QUIRK_DATA_COMPOSITE {
+			{ QUIRK_DATA_IGNORE(0) },
+			{ QUIRK_DATA_STANDARD_MIXER(1) },
+			{ QUIRK_DATA_STANDARD_MIDI(2) },
+			{ QUIRK_DATA_STANDARD_AUDIO(3) },
+			{ QUIRK_DATA_STANDARD_AUDIO(4) },
+			QUIRK_COMPOSITE_END
+		}
+	}
+},
 #undef USB_DEVICE_VENDOR_SPEC
 #undef USB_AUDIO_DEVICE
